metadata.name: Salih - Egypt #1
metadata.description:
The story of Salih is either sad and powerful at the same time. "I was 6 years old when my dad got sick. As last thing before dying he brought me to the desert for the first time ever. It was so intense that I decided to do let it become my job. Everyone should experience this emotion at least once in a lifetime."

We are still in contact with him.

White Desert - Egypt 
March 2019

This NFT comes with an extreme quality print 40x60.
Also 20% of total sale will be donated to him and his family. In eternity, for every future sale.
